Invocation Name: kerala tourist destinations
des:
Find Best tourist places to visit in Kerala. Tourist Destinations in Kerala.

Kerala, a state on India's tropical Malabar Coast, has nearly 600km of Arabian Sea shoreline. It's known for its palm-lined beaches and backwaters, a network of canals.

To start, just say "Alexa, open Kerala Tourist Destinations" or "Alexa, launch Kerala Tourist Destinations".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
